{"tid":1138165,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"胃酸倒流有食開藥/藥劑師請入","createTime":"2019-05-04T10:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T11:11:26.000Z","uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3158885fd4c7e875b83eaf98f889f142ac7d3082","tid":1138165,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"想問下有食開lomac 既brother , 依隻應該點食法？<br />\n利申 照過胃鏡，確診胃酸倒流<br />\n開頭醫生開Pariet 比我，個胃喇住痛，隔日換左dexilant +嘉胃斯康extra 比我<br />\n食左兩個禮拜，太貴無睇落去<br />\n<br />\n近排半夜胃酸特別多，訓唔好，爬文見到lomac omeprazole 依款藥,但唔太知一日食一次定兩次，每次一粒定兩粒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af4bbf90cbc52fcab46c8aff41095294b1eebf2","tid":1138165,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e07efaffaab35bbba475c5164e7804b3dcc0c9","tid":1138165,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21a7c3d3c31e3ae4cecd20477bb773e10d3f1e6","tid":1138165,"uid":203774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"食梳打餅啦"},{"pid":"41df94cd7def4a52f9049c4b37c23e0bbbf07201","tid":1138165,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T11:11:26.000Z","msg":"Pariet (rabeprazole)同omeprazole都係同一個系列嘅藥(PPI) 所以如果Pariet都冇用嘅話omeprazole相信都唔會有用 同埋都要睇下胃酸倒流嘅成因 如果係胃潰瘍就可能要食埋其他藥（抗生素）"}]}